1. *Povodom* nacionalnog praznika, organizovano je prijem u palati. (In honor of the national holiday, a reception was organized in the palace.)

2. Gradonačelnik je izdao izjavu *povodom* ekonomskih problema. (The mayor issued a statement concerning economic problems.)

3. *Povodom* ovog slučaja, pokrenuta je istraga. (In connection with this case, an investigation was launched.)

4. Takmičenje je održano *povodom* Dana grada. (The competition was held on the occasion of the City Day.) 

5. *Povodom* ovog događaja, održana je konferencija za štampu. (In connection with this event, a press conference was held.)